(firstQuint)The Effect of Metformin on Obesity and Metabolic Disturbance in Patients Taking Clozapine.

 In this study, the investigators are going to examine the effect of metformin on obesity and metabolic disturbance in patients with schizophrenia who have taken clozapine.

The metformin 500mg will be administrated per oral twice a day for 24 weeks and for control group, placebo will be given same route and process.

